    \#_dummies_
    id  name     name_es        name_pl
    1  Epiphany  Saimon (es)    Saimon (pl)
    2  Socks     Epifania (es)  Epifania (pl)
    
    \#_epifanias_
    id  name  surnames  name_es      surnames_es  name_pl       surnames_pl
